Subject: Active Directory Scan performance issues
Description: The active directory scan seems to always fail or hang in 6.Activity somewhere. Currently it's stuck at the Group Usage step. Want to see if we can figure out why or what is going on with it. Thanks
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom:
NEA 6.Activity job group not completing as expected.
Cause:
Unable to pull in current data being that NAM is no longer licensed for AD Activity.

Resolution:
Due to a current AD activity Licensing the 6.Activity job group was disable until the NEA NAM license has been updated.
